    <h1>The Rim</h1>
    <p class="lede">The Rim is the edge-place of Vaelinya: a borderland between nearer and farther ways of living, remembering, travelling, and belonging.</p>
    <p>It is a good first place to enter the world because it teaches one of Vaelinya’s core ideas: borders are not only lines. They are places where people meet, cross, carry memory, make agreements, and learn how to notice what changes.</p>
    <p>The people of the Rim are known among themselves as the Rimaeri. Their lives are shaped by movement, weather, memory, careful attention, and the work of keeping connection across difference.</p>
